T1  - THE FEDERAL RESERVE'S IMPLICIT INFLATION TARGET AND MACROECONOMIC DYNAMICS: AN SVAR ANALYSIS
AU  - Mumtaz, Haroon
AU  - Theodoridis, Konstantinos
Y1  - 2023/11/01
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2023/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12638
